room_title: Escape room "Sunken Submarine Tour" by Key To Escape in Nashua
room_description:
You're visiting the newly retired USS George Washington. This submarine was the first of its kind, pioneering a technology so advanced it has yet to be re-created. Your visit takes a quick turn, as the submarine plunges into the river.
The main hatch shuts, sealing out the water, but there's only an hour of oxygen in the emergency reserves. Can you and your fellow submariners find the clues, solve the puzzles, and escape the depths in one hour?
